1:49:05.765-0500","status":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/status/6","description":"The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are closed can be reopened.","iconUrl":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/images/icons/statuses/generic.png","name":"Closed","id":"6","statusCategory":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/statuscategory/3","id":3,"key":"done","colorName":"green","name":"Done"}},"components":[{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/component/10015","id":"10015","name":"Walrus"}],"timeoriginalestimate":null,"customfield_13000":null,"description":"After a restart of the physical machines, I started the DRBD service and mounted the device /dev/drbd1 on the Primary DRBD node.  After that, I started Eucalyptus by hand.  Walrus failed to go into an ENABLED state on the Primary DRBD node.  Error in cloud-error.log:\r\n\r\n{code}\r\nMon Dec 17 06:04:57 2012 ERROR [Component:Eucalyptus.bootstrap:EphemeralConfiguration:arn:euca:bootstrap:Topology::external/.class java.util.concurrent.ThreadPoolExecutor$Worker#21] [com.eucalyptus.component.Component$ComponentBootstrapper.doTransition(Component.java):613] java.lang.RuntimeException: Unable to unmount /dev/drbd1\r\nMon Dec 17 06:04:58 2012 ERROR [Topology:Eucalyptus.bootstrap:EphemeralConfiguration:arn:euca:bootstrap:Topology::external/.class java.util.concurrent.ThreadPoolExecutor$Worker#21] [com.eucalyptus.component.Topology$TopologyChange.doTopologyChange(Topology.java):1166] CHECK:null  arn:euca:bootstrap:walrus:walrus:iron-flag/ DISABLED->DISABLED=NOTREADY [Unable to unmount /dev/drbd1]\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nThe workaround was to unmount the device /dev/drbd1.  After that, Walrus then\r\nwent into ENABLED mode on the Primary DRBD node.   ","customfield_13200":null,"customfield_11300":"PRD-27","customfield_11500":null,"timetracking":{},"customfield_10401":null,"customfield_10005":null,"customfield_10600":null,"customfield_12900":null,"aggregate